          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "A creature entering the aura must succeed at a DC 26 Fortitude save or become sickened 1 until the end of its turn (sickened 2 on a critical failure). While within the aura, an affected creature takes a \u20132 circumstance penalty to recover from the sickened condition. A creature that succeeds at its save is temporarily immune for 1 minute.",
